description: Introducing the Blurex Slim Folio case for the Asus MeMo Pad ME301T. From the best selling brand in tablet cases.Blurex is obsessed about quality, sourcing only the best material and craftsmanship to produce top of the line products.Our products go through rigorous and individual testing before we offer them for saleWe understand you want to protect your investment from scratches and accidental drops yet still have that executive look. We are proud to offer the new BLUREX Leather case for the Asus MeMo Pad ME301T. Made from litchi grain Leather and is handcrafted with meticulous attention detail that meet the BLUREX standards.It includes a built in stand feature that allows you to convert the case into a stand,by slanting the tablet into one if the four ridges.It also has all the necessary cutouts for easy access to all the cameras and ports.
title: Blurex Slim Folio case for Asus ASUS MeMO Pad Smart ME301T
